description: Nashville's first name in frozen treats has made its way to Memphis, and they're bringing shaved ice like you won't believe! Fluffy, flavorful, refreshing cups of shaved ice are being accompanied by a unique Caribbean-themed adventure. Perfect for parties, fundraisers, movie nights, and more, Polar Tropical Shaved Ice is sure to be something you'll never forget!
name: Polar Tropical Shaved Ice & Sweet Treats - Memphis
